data.description: AWESOME LAKE VIEWS! Spacious, bright, updated large 1 BR/1BA East Lakeview condo overlooking Lake Michigan and Lincoln Park. Unit features unobstructed East views of lake, Big windows in both Living Room and in Bedroom, Hardwood floors in living room, tons of great closet space. Building features: 24 hour Door Staff and Maintenance Staff, Fitness Room, Bike Room, new Rooftop Sun Deck, Large Laundry Room, Convenience Store, Dry Cleaner, Valet Garage Pkg. Monthly assessments cover all utilities: heat, water, even electric plus reserved storage locker and basic cable. Freshly painted, new carpet. Sold as-is. Lakeshore Drive and CTA express buses to downtown out front door. Walk to Redline, Wrigley Field, Whole Foods or Jewel, Starbucks, tons of restaurants. Steps to the lake front running/bike trail, Golf course, Montrose Beach and Harbor, Dog Beach, and so so much more.  Prime location!! You will love living here!! FHA approved too!
